        "authorId" : "30fc1801-f8f1-4cc4-9690-e31e203f4f6d",
        "body" : "mostly because i thought that was the 'new norm', but also because these are easier to expand and less subject to other vars/effects created in same invocation.",
        "createdAt" : "2020-04-22T19:01:29Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2020-04-22T19:01:29Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "30fc1801-f8f1-4cc4-9690-e31e203f4f6d",
        "tags" : [
        ]
