        "authorId" : "30fc1801-f8f1-4cc4-9690-e31e203f4f6d",
        "body" : "but all tests for playbook would have to be in same role, that is what i meant. But if this posses a problem i'm fine with changing it, just confused since lately you had advised me to use runme.sh type tests.",
