        "authorId" : "380aef6a-3fbb-41ad-819b-bada96e05807",
        "body" : "If you're planning on adding additional tests in separate playbooks for this target, then using a script makes sense. I was mainly asking because right now there's just the one ansible-playbook invocation, so no benefit to using a script.",
